32:21.667 --> 32:23.732
SO, WHY DIDN'T YOU JUST BREAK UP
WITH ME WHEN I QUIT THE TOUR?

32:23.734 --> 32:25.699
BECAUSE I DIDN'T KNOW
IF I WANTED TO.

32:27.800 --> 32:30.332
BUT I'M SURE NOW.
WE'RE DONE.

32:33.000 --> 32:34.132
GO HOME.

