33:09.734 --> 33:12.898
Rochelle: NOW THAT THIS WHOLE
TAX THING IS ABOUT TO BLOW,

33:12.900 --> 33:15.498
THAT OLD MAN AIN'T GONNA KNOW
WHETHER'S HE'S COMING OR GOING.

33:15.500 --> 33:18.132
