CHILD,
I GOT CONNECTIONS,

33:30.867 --> 33:33.065
AND WE KNOW THIS WORLD
IS RUN ON MONEY.

33:33.067 --> 33:34.265
[ CRUNCHES ]

33:34.267 --> 33:36.998
YOU GOT JACOB RUNNING
AROUND HERE LIKE A PUPPY,

33:37.000 --> 33:39.465
BUYING DIAMONDS.

33:39.467 --> 33:41.765
OLDEST TRICK IN THE BOOK.
THAT WASN'T A TRICK.

33:41.767 --> 33:44.665
MM.
NO, I WAS TRYING TO HELP.

33:44.667 --> 33:46.765
AH. OKAY.

33:49.267 --> 33:50.665
WHOSE SIDE ARE YOU ON?

33:52.000 --> 33:53.599
DON'T YOU EVER WORRY?

33:53.601 --> 33:54.865
ABOUT WHAT?

33:54.867 --> 33:56.465
ABOUT GOD?

33:56.467 --> 33:58.465
YOUR SOUL?

33:58.467 --> 33:59.932
<i> MY</i> SOUL?

33:59.934 --> 34:01.865
YOU GOT EVERYTHING
THAT YOU WANT.

34:01.867 --> 34:03.665
WHY DO THIS?

34:03.667 --> 34:05.465
TASHA...

34:05.467 --> 34:08.665
JAMES GREENLEAF
KILLED MY FATHER

34:08.667 --> 34:10.932
BY BURNING DOWN
HIS OWN CHURCH...

34:10.934 --> 34:12.932
FOR A CHECK --

34:12.934 --> 34:15.665
A LOUSY CHECK
FROM AN INSURANCE MAN.

34:15.667 --> 34:17.398
I JUST THINK THAT --

34:17.400 --> 34:19.465
IT WASN'T
JUST BASIE'S FATHER.

34:19.467 --> 34:20.932
I KNOW.
HE WAS YOURS, TOO.

34:20.934 --> 34:23.399
OKAY, SO DON'T QUESTION ME
ABOUT MY SOUL.

34:23.401 --> 34:25.032
DO I MAKE MYSELF CLEAR?

34:27.700 --> 34:28.765
GREENLEAF'S
BEEN AROUND HERE

34:28.767 --> 34:31.399
MAKING A MOCKERY OF RELIGION
FOR TWO GENERATIONS.

34:32.867 --> 34:34.465
HELL,

34:34.467 --> 34:37.065
YOU KEEP THAT LITTLE HIGH-YELLOW
THING OF GRACE'S AROUND,

34:37.067 --> 34:38.265
MAKE IT THREE.

34:39.934 --> 34:42.265
LOOK, WE'RE ON
THE RIGHT SIDE OF THIS.

34:42.267 --> 34:44.998
WE JUST HAVE
TO STAY THE COURSE.

34:45.000 --> 34:47.198
YOU HEAR ME?
I HEAR YOU.

34:47.200 --> 34:51.865
♪♪

34:51.867 --> 34:53.532
GOOD.

34:53.534 --> 34:55.465
'CAUSE I AIN'T GOT NO TIME
FOR NO BACKSLIDING.

34:56.667 --> 34:58.398
WE JUST GOT
TO KEEP THE FAITH.

34:58.400 --> 35:06.065
