HEAR IT FROM ME.

35:13.867 --> 35:15.932
KEVIN, IT'S FINE.
REALLY, I MEAN...

35:15.934 --> 35:18.099
I'M MOVING ON, TOO.

35:18.101 --> 35:19.698
CHARITY, WHERE ARE YOU
AT RIGHT NOW?

35:19.700 --> 35:21.565
