35:59.001 --> 36:02.932
AND WHILE EVERYBODY ELSE
COMES TO WORSHIP, REFLECT,

36:02.934 --> 36:04.265
AND FOR SOME PEOPLE,
THEY JUST COME HERE

36:04.267 --> 36:05.532
TO TRY TO GET AWAY
FROM THEIR KIDS

36:05.534 --> 36:06.798
FOR AS LONG AS
THEY POSSIBLY CAN.

36:06.800 --> 36:09.398
