YOU DIDN'T GO TO CHURCH.

36:32.867 --> 36:36.132
WELL, I'M NOT
HERE TO WORSHIP.

36:36.134 --> 36:39.465
YOU HAVE SOME NEWS
ABOUT ROCHELLE?

36:39.467 --> 36:41.598
SHE CHECKS OUT, GRACE.

36:41.600 --> 36:43.499
THAT CAN'T BE TRUE.

36:43.501 --> 36:45.465
THE ACTUAL REASON I'M HERE...

36:45.467 --> 36:47.131
WHAT ELSE?
SOMEONE AT THE IRS

36:47.133 --> 36:49.832
JUST RELEASED A MEMO --
A LIST OF ALL THESE MEGACHURCHES

36:49.834 --> 36:52.698
WHOSE PASTORS
HAVEN'T BEEN PAYING TAXES

36:52.700 --> 36:54.998
ON THEIR PERSONAL INCOME.

36:55.000 --> 36:56.865
APPARENTLY, THERE'S SOME GUY
ON THE INSIDE AT THE IRS

36:56.867 --> 37:00.131
THAT'S BEEN CUTTING DEALS
WITH ON THESE CHURCHES

37:00.133 --> 37:01.965
FOR A FEE.

37:01.967 --> 37:04.365
CALVARY'S ON THE LIST?

37:04.367 --> 37:05.899
AT THE TOP.

37:05.901 --> 37:09.265
♪♪

37:13.534 --> 37:15.532
Kerissa:
WELL, I WILL HAVE THEM ALL
REVIEWED BY TOMORROW MORNING,

37:15.534 --> 37:18.665
ALL RIGHT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:18.667 --> 37:19.998
UH-HUH.
IS ZORA IN HER ROOM?

37:20.000 --> 37:22.132
OH, MICHELLE, LET ME
CALL YOU BACK. OKAY?

37:23.267 --> 37:24.332
YEAH, WHAT'S UP?

37:26.934 --> 37:29.299
SHE STOLE
THAT MONEY.

37:31.067 --> 37:32.432
OH, BABY, COME HERE.

37:32.434 --> 37:33.598
GO -- GO IN
THE LIVING ROOM, OKAY?

37:33.600 --> 37:35.065
GO AHEAD. GO SIT DOWN.

37:35.067 --> 37:36.532
