37:36.534 --> 37:38.299
ZORA!
WHAT?

37:39.434 --> 37:41.065
ZORA, OPEN THIS DOOR.

37:41.067 --> 37:42.665
JACOB, DON'T DO THIS.

37:42.667 --> 37:44.465
DIDN'T WE TELL HER
NOT TO LOCK THIS DOOR?

37:44.467 --> 37:45.932
WE DID.
OKAY! OKAY!

37:45.934 --> 37:47.798
OPEN THE DOOR!

37:47.800 --> 37:49.332
WHAT? WHAT DO
YOU GUYS WANT?

