38:07.100 --> 38:09.098
-DID YOU TAKE THE --
-NO! I DON'T KNOW WHAT --

38:09.100 --> 38:10.098
CAN YOU PLEASE STOP
GOING THROUGH --

38:10.100 --> 38:11.632
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

38:11.634 --> 38:13.365
I DIDN'T TAKE ANY MONEY. I DON'T
KNOW WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

38:13.367 --> 38:15.498
I DIDN'T TAKE ANY MONEY.
-JACOB, PLEASE!

38:15.500 --> 38:17.632
[ OBJECTS CLATTERING ]

38:17.634 --> 38:20.598
CAN YOU PLEASE STOP
GOING THROUGH MY STUFF?

38:20.600 --> 38:22.232
WHERE IS IT? HUH?

38:27.167 --> 38:28.332
WHERE IS IT?!

38:31.400 --> 38:33.065
JACOB!

38:36.600 --> 38:38.798
