39:01.000 --> 39:04.732
KORYN, I NEED YOU TO ARRANGE
THE PLANE FOR THE 17th,

39:04.734 --> 39:07.299
RETURNING
THAT EVENING, PLEASE.

39:07.301 --> 39:09.198
WHERE TO?

39:09.200 --> 39:11.532
ATLANTA.

39:11.534 --> 39:13.265
