AN OLD FRIEND.

39:13.267 --> 39:15.465
[ KEYS CLACKING ]

39:15.467 --> 39:22.598
♪♪

39:22.600 --> 39:23.999
WHAT IS THIS?

39:25.267 --> 39:27.132
OH, YEAH.

39:27.134 --> 39:29.065
THE REPORTER SAID
SHE HAD A DEADLINE.

39:29.067 --> 39:31.398
GRACE HANDLED IT.

39:31.400 --> 39:40.731
♪♪

39:40.733 --> 39:43.065
MAE?

39:43.067 --> 39:45.299
MAE, I-I-IT WAS
A STUPID MISTAKE.

39:46.733 --> 39:48.399
I WAS TRYING
TO MAKE A POINT, AND I --

39:49.634 --> 39:51.465
I'M SORRY.
DON'T BE.

39:53.467 --> 39:55.765
OH, I'M GLAD
YOU DID IT.

39:55.767 --> 39:58.165
LOOK, LOOK,
DON'T TAKE SUCH A POSITION.

39:58.167 --> 40:00.165
