A HARD LOOK AT MYSELF

40:04.300 --> 40:05.632
AND MY CHOICES...

40:08.067 --> 40:10.332
...AND FOR THAT,
I'M ACTUALLY GRATEFUL.

40:14.000 --> 40:15.831
