40:17.401 --> 40:19.665
WE HAVE TO.
I MEAN, THERE'S...

40:19.667 --> 40:22.265
THERE'S TOO MUCH AT STAKE.
WE CAN'T, JAMES.

40:22.267 --> 40:23.899
LISTEN TO ME.

40:25.434 --> 40:27.698
I FORGIVE YOU,

40:27.700 --> 40:29.098
AND I'M DONE
POINTING FINGERS.

40:29.100 --> 40:30.865
THAT'S OVER.
JUST...

40:32.534 --> 40:34.399
IT'S JUST ME
I CAN'T FORGIVE NOW.

40:36.867 --> 40:38.932
FOR MARRYING YOU

40:38.934 --> 40:42.465
AND MAKING OUR LIFE
MY CALLING

40:42.467 --> 40:45.232
WHEN I KNEW THAT
I WAS CALLED BY GOD.

40:46.967 --> 40:49.332
TO DO WHAT?
WHO KNOWS?

40:51.967 --> 40:53.465
ANYTHING OTHER THAN THIS.

40:54.934 --> 40:58.332
ANYTHING OTHER THAN BEING
AT THE MERCY OF A MAN

40:58.334 --> 41:02.665
WHO PLUCKS AT THE WEB

41:02.667 --> 41:05.832
OF MY ABSURDLY-
CONSTRUCTED LIFE.

41:05.834 --> 41:07.099
NO, LOOK. NO.

41:09.467 --> 41:12.399
MY LAWYER MADE SOME NOTES
IN THE MARGINS AND...

41:14.534 --> 41:16.698
YOU'LL FIGURE IT
ALL OUT.

41:16.700 --> 41:18.332
DON'T DO THIS.

41:18.334 --> 41:20.665
[ BIRDS CHIRPING IN DISTANCE ]

41:26.834 --> 41:30.465
♪♪

41:30.467 --> 41:31.765
I HAVE TO.

41:33.600 --> 41:35.531
IT'S TIME TO GO.

